title: Travel Warning! The Women In Colombia Are Too Hot! Travel At Your Own Risk?!
description:
Ladies, what’s the one country you will never let your spouse visit? And when you think about that place, what about it makes you not want your spouse to go? Is it the precautionary travel advisory? Or is it the women?
Every year, Moe plans a trip out of the country with his friends. This year they’re going to Colombia. He invited all of them and they were all excited until Moe mentioned the location.
